{"tid":2027231,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"冷靜 大家緊記","createTime":"2020-05-21T10:34:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-22T16:32:28.000Z","uid":273593,"like":121,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"cdda498bf790c937c8aa8939e4b41d74604fe91b","tid":2027231,"uid":273593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T10:34:19.000Z","msg":"「黎明前係至撚黑暗」 一句大家都有聽過<br />\n<br />\n大家緊記<br />\n1. <span style=\"color: red;\">沒有一個獨裁政權是永遠存在的</span><br />\n蘇聯倒台解體，東歐劇變，韓國台灣民主化， 歷史證明只要夠膽反抗極權，終得自由。<br />\n<br />\n2. <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">認清敵人</span></span><br />\n中共最鍾意spin走對象<br />\n搞批鬥<br />\n目標係獨裁者唔係平民百姓 <br />\n成功之前之後，都唔好先打一場內戰<br />\n認清敵人<br />\n<br />\n3. <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">伸出援手，勿忘初衷</span></span><br />\n手足，唔係一句稱呼，係一個信念<br />\n有一日可能全面肅清反抗力量<br />\n窩藏手足，提供食物，提供金錢<br />\n千祈唔好各家自掃門前雪<br />\n每一次向人伸出援手<br />\n都係時代革命<br />\n<br />\n4. <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">沒有永遠的敵人</span></span><br />\n嘗試說服，而不是攻擊敵人<br />\n嘗試了解對方立場<br />\n嘗試了解對方苦況<br />\n要相信<br />\n人是會改變<br />\n好多人都有藍轉黃<br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命"},{"pid":"8902c1179e4ff97d5e90b0da1c43670e5a4c7833","tid":2027231,"uid":262406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T10:35:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"430b30e914048b8a336191fba99ca3f9befa4303","tid":2027231,"uid":3776,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T10:43:09.000Z","msg":"光復香港"},{"pid":"8e6ddff771b9cad3b378148e95ac20a20b3e76f9","tid":2027231,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T10:51:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.